{"word":"Seir","slug":"seir","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Seir</b> <a href=\"#/H8165\">H8165</a> <br/> 1. A range of hills trending southwest from the Dead Sea:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=2'>Deu 1:2</a> <br/> - Along the route from Horeb to Kadeshbarnea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=2'>Deu 1:2</a> <br/> - Children of Israel journey by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=2'>Deu 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=1'>Deu 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=2'>Deu 33:2</a> <br/> - Originally inhabited by Horites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=6'>Gen 14:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=30'>Gen 36:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=12'>Deu 2:12</a> <br/> - Later inhabited by the children of Esau after they destroyed the Horim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=12'>Deu 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=22'>Deu 2:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=32&verse=3'>Gen 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=33&verse=14'>Gen 33:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=33&verse=16'>Gen 33:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=9'>Gen 36:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=24&verse=18'>Num 24:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=5'>Deu 2:5</a> <br/> - The southern boundary of the conquests of Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=18'>Jos 11:18</a> <br/> 2. A Horite chief<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=21'>Gen 36:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=38'>1Ch 1:38</a>"}]}